# ADR-005: Command and Service Separation

## Status

Accepted

## Context

VS Code commands directly accessing AI services would create tightly coupled code.

## Decision

Commands will only orchestrate user interactions.

Business operations must be implemented inside services.

Example:

Command:

generateEmbedding.ts

Service:

huggingfaceService.ts

## Consequences

Positive:

- Improved testability
- Easier replacement of dependencies
- Cleaner architecture

Negative:

- More abstraction layers
